title: Ep. 305 - Trump Is Right About Baltimore
description:
Today on the show, President Trump says Baltimore is a dump. His observation is factually correct. But is it racist? Democrats says so. Also, a mother complains about childless millennials ruining Disney world. Should grown ups without kids be banned from theme parks? We will tackle that important question today. Date: 07-29-2019
